PROJECT CONTEXT

The system being developed is an Internal Admin Portal for a cinema chain called CineVillage.

This portal will be used by cinema managers to manage cinema operations including:

• Cinema halls
• Movie listings
• Screening schedules
• Operational dashboard

The system is part of a two-phase architecture:

Phase 1:
Admin Portal (current assignment)

Phase 2:
Customer-facing booking app that will rely entirely on this backend system.

Therefore data integrity and business rule correctness are critical.

