endTime
date

----------------------------------------------

CRITICAL BUSINESS RULE

Screenings must NOT overlap within the same hall.

Example:

Movie A duration = 120 minutes
Start time = 2:00 PM

That hall cannot schedule another movie between:

2:00 PM and 4:00 PM

----------------------------------------------

OVERLAP DETECTION LOGIC

When creating a screening, the system must check:

existingStart < newEnd
AND
existingEnd > newStart

If this condition is true:

The scheduling request must be rejected.

This logic must also correctly handle:

• different dates
• time boundaries
• timezone consistency

----------------------------------------------

MODULE 5: DASHBOARD

The dashboard page must display:

• total active movies
• number of screenings scheduled today
• list of upcoming screenings

Upcoming screenings must be sorted chronologically.

